Compile "heartbeat.cpp":
-----
g++ -o heartbeat heartbeat.cpp


Setup heartbeat:
-----
cd /sys/class/gpio
echo 204 > export
cd gpio204
echo out > direction


Start heartbeat on boot (ODroid):
-----
1) setup heartbeat (as above)
2) put "heartbeat_start.sh" in /etc/init.d
3) put "heartbeat" (executable) in home directory
3) cd /etc/init.d
4) chmod +x heartbeat_start.sh
5) update-rc.d heartbeat_start.sh defaults


Start WagMan script on boot (ODroid):
-----
1) put "WagMan_start.sh" in /etc/init.d
2) put "WagMan.py" in home directory
3) cd /etc/init.d
4) chmod +x WagMan_start.sh
5) update-rc.d WagMan_start.sh defaults
6) install pyserial
7) put "99-usb-serial.rules" in /etc/udev/rules.d